08:57.641 --> 09:00.197
♪ Even if there are
thousands of beauties and affairs ♪

09:00.197 --> 09:03.368
♪ All turn to nothing ♪

09:03.368 --> 09:09.413
♪ In this life,
my spirit is still untamed ♪

09:09.413 --> 09:12.456
♪ Even if the country is ruined ♪

09:12.456 --> 09:15.587
♪ With never-ending wars
