09:15.587 --> 09:21.064
♪ I am willing to shed the splendid dress
and wear the armor ♪

09:21.064 --> 09:28.287
♪ In the vast world,
I will do whatever I like ♪

09:28.311 --> 09:39.031
- Linglong!
- Linglong!

09:39.031 --> 09:42.411
Next, let's welcome Wang Ke.

09:44.470 --> 09:46.531
Hello, everyone. I am Wang Ke.

09:48.110 --> 09:50.330
Please clap louder.

09:52.896 --> 09:54.184
♪ The northern wind comes ♪

09:54.184 --> 09:55.405
♪ The raging waves of long history ♪

09:55.405 --> 09:56.104
♪ The moon shines ♪

09:56.104 --> 09:58.069
♪ Victorious kings
and blood-soaked cities ♪

09:58.069 --> 09:59.272
♪ Changes under the beacon flames ♪

09:59.272 --> 10:00.433
♪ Until the table is turned ♪

10:00.433 --> 10:01.192
♪ I am ready ♪

10:01.192 --> 10:03.055
♪ The killing intention
is seen through instantly ♪

10:03.055 --> 10:05.224
♪ The bonfire is blazing
Ignite the smoke signal ♪

10:05.224 --> 10:06.216
♪ Hero's farewell ♪

10:06.216 --> 10:08.167
♪ Meet each other in front of the lineup ♪

10:08.167 --> 10:09.276
♪ Laughing at sand like snow ♪

10:09.276 --> 10:10.280
♪ It's me, holding the sword ♪

10:10.280 --> 10:11.349
♪ A chest full of passion ♪

10:11.349 --> 10:14.012
♪ Spilled towards the world
of buried bones ♪

10:15.110 --> 10:18.191
- Wang Ke! Wang Ke!
- Wang Ke! Wang Ke!

10:18.191 --> 10:28.040
♪ The world changes, heroes are no more ♪

10:28.590 --> 10:29.931
Thank you.

10:31.791 --> 10:35.090
Next, let's welcome Qiang Qingci.

10:36.608 --> 10:38.235
♪ Looking north at the rivers ♪

10:38.235 --> 10:42.460
♪ Unable to see through
the extensive streams ♪

10:43.230 --> 10:44.931
Here he comes.

10:45.022 --> 10:48.680
♪ Send me up to the vast heavens ♪

10:48.680 --> 10:51.543
♪ A thousand miles by boat
crossing heavy mountains ♪

10:51.543 --> 10:53.892
♪ Wind pushes on, rain turns cold ♪

10:53.892 --> 10:55.304
♪ This life is full of turns ♪

10:55.304 --> 11:00.656
♪ Difficult times reveal true courage ♪

11:00.680 --> 11:02.216
♪ Looking north at the rivers ♪

11:02.238 --> 11:05.774
♪ Where the setting sun sits
are limitless landscapes ♪

11:05.774 --> 11:08.904
♪ The north wind passes
the critical gate ♪

11:08.904 --> 11:12.680
♪ Should not refuse a fight ♪

11:12.680 --> 11:14.120
♪ Day and night are vast ♪

11:14.120 --> 11:15.592
♪ Into a chessboard ♪

11:15.592 --> 11:17.800
♪ Decisive moves brightly made ♪

11:17.800 --> 11:23.784
♪ Through the ages,
epochs roll thunderously by ♪

11:23.784 --> 11:36.168
♪ Through the ages,
epochs roll thunderously by ♪

11:36.951 --> 11:40.010
He is so suitable for
this kind of desolate song.

11:41.391 --> 11:45.411
The recorders wrote down
my killings in this life.

11:46.391 --> 11:51.531
Please let me paint your face
under the palace lamp.

11:52.431 --> 11:53.811
As is initially.

11:55.151 --> 11:56.571
As is originally.

12:00.750 --> 12:03.806
All friends on the scene and online,

12:03.830 --> 12:09.367
all the bonus sessions ended.

12:09.391 --> 12:12.047
Once again, thank you all
for your participation.

12:12.071 --> 12:13.850
Thank you everyone.

12:19.021 --> 12:22.044
(Girl's Dorm Building 3)

12:40.791 --> 12:41.891
(Are you busy?)

12:55.031 --> 12:58.051
(Yeah, some things.)

12:59.391 --> 13:00.970
(Go ahead.)

13:07.630 --> 13:09.486
(Play by yourself for a while.)

13:09.510 --> 13:11.010
(I'll call you when I finish.)

13:11.710 --> 13:12.850
(Okay.)

13:26.975 --> 13:29.756
(Girl's Dorm Building 3)

13:45.157 --> 13:47.726
(Mo Qingcheng)

13:47.750 --> 13:49.966
(I wrap up, but it's too late.)

13:49.990 --> 13:52.490
(I won't call you then. Good night.)

13:52.750 --> 13:55.171
(Or, good morning.)

14:02.911 --> 14:04.210
Missing a boy?

14:05.311 --> 14:07.647
No. "Missing him."

14:07.671 --> 14:09.531
Go away.

14:17.671 --> 14:19.411
Working the night shift again.

14:20.071 --> 14:22.127
I came temporarily.

14:22.151 --> 14:24.127
How is the patient in bed nineteen?

14:24.151 --> 14:25.047
Pretty good.

14:25.071 --> 14:27.566
He's being discharged and waiting for
his family to pick him up.

14:27.590 --> 14:29.370
Is he your friend's family?

14:29.750 --> 14:31.086
My friend's grandpa.

14:31.110 --> 14:32.571
Zhao.

14:38.671 --> 14:40.370
Discuss something with you.

14:41.990 --> 14:44.326
May I leave the hospital on my own?

14:44.350 --> 14:45.686
It's a weekday.

14:45.710 --> 14:49.527
It's not appropriate for the kids
to take time off to get me.

14:49.551 --> 14:50.686
That won't do.

14:50.710 --> 14:53.647
You're a doctor yourself.
You should understand.

14:53.671 --> 14:55.407
If your family doesn't come,

14:55.431 --> 14:56.767
and given your age,

14:56.791 --> 14:58.887
how could we possibly let you go?

14:58.911 --> 15:00.771
Alright. I'll listen to you.

15:16.391 --> 15:16.966
Morning.

15:16.990 --> 15:18.490
Hi, Doudou.

15:22.791 --> 15:25.210
You alone? Where are they?

15:27.830 --> 15:30.691
Mr. Mo is taking a nap inside.

15:34.350 --> 15:36.250
I'm really worried.

15:37.151 --> 15:39.527
He finally got a girlfriend.

15:39.551 --> 15:40.927
He has surgeries today, then tomorrow.

15:40.951 --> 15:42.326
Overnight shift the day after tomorrow

15:42.350 --> 15:44.927
and then the hospital
calls him back again.

15:44.951 --> 15:48.811
Eventually, the girlfriend will be gone.

15:51.151 --> 15:52.250
What do you have?

15:55.271 --> 15:56.726
I'll pass. I'm leaving.

15:56.750 --> 15:57.686
Where are you going?

15:57.710 --> 16:00.446
I, well, have to go to the company.

16:00.470 --> 16:02.686
I bought a lot today. Have some.

16:02.710 --> 16:04.271
I'll pass. This is enough for me.

16:04.271 --> 16:05.571
Take a cup of soy milk.

16:14.071 --> 16:15.846
I-I have to attend PE class.

16:15.870 --> 16:18.891
Where is the contract?
Give it to me and I'll sign it.

16:19.191 --> 16:21.007
Where's your PE class? Is it far?

16:21.031 --> 16:22.806
Yes. It takes ten minutes to get there.

16:22.830 --> 16:24.326
I'll sign the contract.

16:24.350 --> 16:27.250
How about I give you a ride?

16:28.391 --> 16:29.927
Stop it. Let's go. Get in the car.

16:29.951 --> 16:31.651
Aren't you running out of time? Go.

16:32.510 --> 16:33.750
T-Thank you.

16:33.750 --> 16:34.527
Let's go.

16:34.551 --> 16:35.730
Thank you.

16:39.431 --> 16:40.767
(What happened?)

16:40.791 --> 16:43.411
(He drives me
to attend even PE class.)

16:45.470 --> 16:47.370
Buckle your seatbelt, will you?

16:48.230 --> 16:49.127
Need a hand?

16:49.151 --> 16:51.171
No, thanks. I am good.

16:53.671 --> 16:56.570
- Just tell me how to get there.
- Alright.

17:20.911 --> 17:22.966
I caught up. Thank you so much.

17:22.990 --> 17:26.091
- I'll be leaving.
- All right.

17:27.550 --> 17:28.526
The contract.

17:28.550 --> 17:31.010
I'll sign it for you after class.

17:53.831 --> 17:55.691
Help me press it down again.

18:22.470 --> 18:24.490
(Why do you have PE exams
in your senior year?)

18:27.710 --> 18:29.807
(It's an exceptional case.)

18:29.831 --> 18:31.371
Geng Xiaoxing.

18:31.911 --> 18:33.290
I'm here.

18:33.631 --> 18:35.891
- I'm going over there.
- Okay.

18:36.911 --> 18:37.847
Came for the exam?

18:37.871 --> 18:39.686
You've done that paper.

18:39.710 --> 18:41.451
Just finish these two tests.

18:41.550 --> 18:43.006
Thank you, Sir.

18:43.030 --> 18:44.451
Go. Start with the ball.

19:02.831 --> 19:04.931
(What to eat tonight?)

19:14.151 --> 19:15.431
(I still have a class today.)

19:15.431 --> 19:17.171
(I can't go home until tonight.)

19:20.990 --> 19:21.990
Really?

19:28.351 --> 19:30.050
What are you doing here?

19:30.510 --> 19:31.810
I took a rest today.

19:34.030 --> 19:35.686
Came to accompany you for class.

19:35.710 --> 19:38.210
Have a meal, then go home.

19:39.270 --> 19:41.490
How did you know I attend this class?

19:42.310 --> 19:43.730
I got your schedule.

19:46.270 --> 19:47.411
The teacher.

19:52.191 --> 19:54.970
(Luckily, it's an optional course
and no one knows each other.)

19:56.470 --> 19:57.470
Students, wait a moment.

19:57.470 --> 19:59.810
I'm going to upload the materials.

20:14.750 --> 20:15.550
(Pretend.)

20:15.550 --> 20:17.286
(It's an optional course.
It doesn't matter.)

20:17.310 --> 20:20.526
Today, we will appreciate
a gunfight action movie.

20:20.550 --> 20:21.807
While watching,

20:21.831 --> 20:22.631
pay attention

20:22.631 --> 20:25.411
to the coordination between
the rhythm of the music and the screen.

20:25.591 --> 20:26.191
Wait a moment.

20:26.191 --> 20:27.316
(Black and White)

20:27.340 --> 20:30.898
(Qiang Qingci dubbed Cheng Muyun,
March 28, 2020)

20:31.591 --> 20:33.807
The movie we're going to appreciate

20:33.831 --> 20:35.570
is a gunfight action movie.

20:36.831 --> 20:37.550
While watching,

20:37.550 --> 20:38.431
notice the rhythm.

20:38.431 --> 20:42.451
Could you help me
with the curtain later?

20:42.550 --> 20:43.810
Sure.

21:09.310 --> 21:10.966
Congratulations on your graduation.

21:10.990 --> 21:11.766
Amazing.

21:11.790 --> 21:13.206
Thank you, Sir. Thank you.

21:13.230 --> 21:14.451
You are the best.

21:18.591 --> 21:21.131
Go ahead. Your boyfriend
has been waiting for a long time.

21:21.911 --> 21:23.510
No, no. He's not my boyfriend.

21:23.510 --> 21:25.550
H-He is just a friend, Sir.

21:25.550 --> 21:28.050
Go ahead. You've finished the exam.

21:28.591 --> 21:29.770
Thank you, Sir.

21:30.030 --> 21:31.651
- Goodbye, Sir.
- Bye-bye.

21:32.191 --> 21:33.951
Goodbye. I passed. Goodbye.

21:33.951 --> 21:34.486
Goodbye.

21:34.510 --> 21:36.131
Next student.

21:38.270 --> 21:39.931
In the blue shirt, come on.

21:41.310 --> 21:43.131
Have a rest here.

21:47.151 --> 21:48.411
The exam is over.

21:49.030 --> 21:50.371
Finally, it is over.

21:51.030 --> 21:52.171
Thank you.

21:52.671 --> 21:54.286
Thanks for driving me here.

21:54.310 --> 21:56.050
Otherwise, I would have failed.

21:56.431 --> 21:58.091
Finally finished the exam.

22:00.070 --> 22:03.210
Why did you need to take PE exams
even in your senior year?

22:04.790 --> 22:06.966
I went on an exchange
during my sophomore and junior year.

22:06.990 --> 22:08.367
I didn't get a chance to take it.

22:08.391 --> 22:10.131
So it had to be moved to now.

22:18.871 --> 22:19.891
Thank you.

22:32.111 --> 22:34.371
Is there any place I didn't clean?

22:37.151 --> 22:39.010
Here. A little bit.

22:48.510 --> 22:51.770
Let me sign the contract.

22:52.030 --> 22:53.766
The contract is in the car.

22:53.790 --> 22:56.091
Have a rest. We can get it later.

22:56.990 --> 22:59.046
Cool. After I rest,

22:59.070 --> 23:01.570
- I'll go with you.
- Okay.

23:04.030 --> 23:05.726
If I knew you were taking PE,

23:05.750 --> 23:08.371
I would have bought you a bubble tea.

23:08.671 --> 23:10.770
I'm okay. I'm not thirsty.

23:14.911 --> 23:16.651
I'd better go buy one.

23:21.310 --> 23:25.050
I mean I have already finished the exam.

23:25.191 --> 23:26.970
I'll go with you and get it.

23:28.911 --> 23:30.490
Okay. Let's go then.

23:31.591 --> 23:32.730
Alright.

23:41.550 --> 23:42.611
Tired, huh?

23:43.391 --> 23:44.570
A little.

24:17.391 --> 24:21.171
Isn't this course
Western Classical Music History?

24:21.550 --> 24:22.691
Lights off?

24:23.111 --> 24:27.091
The teacher changed it last minute
to Film and TV Masterpiece Appreciation.

24:27.591 --> 24:30.691
- Coincidence. We can watch the movie.
- That sounds good.

24:32.310 --> 24:34.927
Sir, I can't see clearly.
May I change my seat?

24:34.951 --> 24:36.131
Yes.

24:36.351 --> 24:38.006
The students who need to change seats.

24:38.030 --> 24:41.210
Please do it now,
so you won't have to get up later.

24:48.030 --> 24:49.171
Excuse me.

24:50.911 --> 24:51.686
Thank you.

24:51.710 --> 24:52.970
You're welcome.

24:56.631 --> 24:59.327
Can we eat snacks, Sir?

24:59.351 --> 25:01.087
How about getting you some popcorn?

25:01.111 --> 25:03.206
I think I should prepare well
for you next time.

25:03.230 --> 25:05.010
For those who want to date,

25:05.111 --> 25:07.167
you can do it after class,

25:07.191 --> 25:10.490
but when it comes to watching movies,
we need to stay serious.

25:14.351 --> 25:16.210
Why are they all looking at me?

25:48.591 --> 25:52.050
Mr. Mo was called back
to the hospital again?

25:52.871 --> 25:55.131
I think he went to find Sheng.

25:55.510 --> 25:57.611
What a steel will.

26:02.070 --> 26:06.611
He's already handsome and yet still
pursues love with a fighting spirit.

26:09.191 --> 26:10.611
Where's Juemei?

26:10.671 --> 26:12.407
He said he went to sign a contract.

26:12.431 --> 26:14.530
It should be a company matter.

26:15.111 --> 26:19.250
He's so rich now. Can't he take a break?

26:30.230 --> 26:32.611
Are you busy these days?

26:34.550 --> 26:36.891
Not really. Chill.

26:37.310 --> 26:40.131
I've completed all the credit hours.
I'm just waiting to graduate.

26:40.831 --> 26:43.006
I took the optional class today

26:43.030 --> 26:45.966
because there are not many
serious classes this semester.

26:45.990 --> 26:47.050
Randomly.

26:47.351 --> 26:49.167
That course is actually fun.

26:49.191 --> 26:51.810
He makes each class
sound like a stand-up comedy.

26:54.591 --> 26:56.331
I thought you were really busy.

26:57.631 --> 26:59.210
Why?

27:00.391 --> 27:04.891
When I checked my phone after work,
I didn't find any messages from you.

27:05.591 --> 27:09.411
I didn't know what to send.

27:10.431 --> 27:12.970
I thought we could chat at any time.

27:17.591 --> 27:19.246
Before...

27:19.270 --> 27:21.570
Now there's nothing to chat about?

27:25.191 --> 27:29.210
What are you doing here today?

27:29.990 --> 27:32.411
What else could I be doing here?

27:33.310 --> 27:34.951
I mean, besides finding me,

27:34.951 --> 27:37.290
is there anything else you need to do?

27:37.391 --> 27:40.570
Do I need to do anything else
besides finding you?

27:44.470 --> 27:47.891
(Canteen 3)
Did you bring me to eat at the canteen?

27:47.990 --> 27:50.810
No. I didn't think too much
and came over here.

27:50.990 --> 27:52.407
Let me treat you at the canteen.

27:52.431 --> 27:54.486
Our school has a Xinjiang restaurant.

27:54.510 --> 27:58.127
- Their saute spicy chicken is yummy.
- Sounds good.

27:58.151 --> 27:59.530
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

28:04.951 --> 28:06.810
The saute spicy chicken is sold out.

28:08.351 --> 28:10.851
It's alright. We can eat this.

28:11.191 --> 28:12.927
Come earlier next time.

28:12.951 --> 28:14.010
Sure.

28:16.831 --> 28:18.570
You like saute spicy chicken?

28:19.951 --> 28:21.087
I could make it for you.

28:21.111 --> 28:22.127
Great.

28:22.151 --> 28:24.091
You can even cook saute spicy chicken.

28:24.470 --> 28:25.530
Yes, I can.

28:28.191 --> 28:30.290
Why do you like cooking?

28:31.871 --> 28:33.327
When I was a kid, my parents were busy.

28:33.351 --> 28:36.530
I had nothing to do at home,
so I started learning to cook.

28:36.790 --> 28:39.171
Then I cooked better and better.

28:39.351 --> 28:41.686
They began taking the meals
I prepared to the hospital.

28:41.710 --> 28:45.730
Later, I often cooked for them.

28:46.470 --> 28:48.010
Such a dutiful person.

28:48.671 --> 28:49.970
Dutiful?

28:50.470 --> 28:54.010
No. It's gifted.

28:55.310 --> 28:57.206
My parents were busy when I was young.

28:57.230 --> 28:58.807
So, I lived with my grandfather.

28:58.831 --> 29:00.931
I wanted to learn to cook myself.

29:01.111 --> 29:03.250
However,

29:03.431 --> 29:08.050
my cooking has an indescribable taste.

29:09.070 --> 29:11.490
I kind of want to give it a try.

29:18.351 --> 29:22.290
What plans do you have after dinner?

29:23.030 --> 29:26.331
- None.
- Me neither.

29:27.990 --> 29:32.451
- Let's find something to do later.
- Okay.

29:38.070 --> 29:42.851
What did you do on your dates?

29:51.270 --> 29:52.570
I have never dated.

29:55.030 --> 29:56.131
Really?

29:56.790 --> 29:57.810
Yeah.

29:59.111 --> 30:01.691
- What about you?
- The same.

30:01.790 --> 30:05.050
Like you, I have never dated.

30:09.671 --> 30:11.327
Why are you laughing?

30:11.351 --> 30:15.371
Isn't it normal for me
given I am younger than you?

30:15.831 --> 30:16.931
Indeed.

30:32.631 --> 30:33.931
No worries.

30:34.391 --> 30:37.127
I can make saute spicy chicken
anytime you feel like eating it.

30:37.151 --> 30:40.371
- The taste won't be worse than here.
- Okay.

30:45.070 --> 30:47.607
- What's wrong?
- I forgot it.

30:47.631 --> 30:49.526
I have to clean the studio today.

30:49.550 --> 30:50.891
The studio?

30:51.470 --> 30:54.286
We rented a place in an old community

30:54.310 --> 30:56.570
and renovated it into
a recording studio.

30:56.831 --> 30:59.367
Of course, it can't be compared
with your Tianzi No. 1 Recording Studio.

30:59.391 --> 31:00.167
We just started it.

31:00.191 --> 31:03.010
Today is my turn to clean.

31:04.790 --> 31:06.891
They always go on time.

31:07.351 --> 31:09.607
How about I drop you
at the subway station

31:09.631 --> 31:11.371
before I go clean it?

31:11.671 --> 31:12.770
I'll go with you.

31:14.750 --> 31:15.647
It isn't suitable.

31:15.671 --> 31:17.486
You came all this way to be with me

31:17.510 --> 31:19.327
and I'm having you watch me clean.

31:19.351 --> 31:21.091
I came to meet you today.

31:21.191 --> 31:23.490
Anything else doesn't matter.

31:24.710 --> 31:27.331
- Let's go. Take me with you.
- Let's go.

31:34.351 --> 31:35.530
Here is it.

31:35.911 --> 31:37.891
The colored glass part
on the second floor.

31:38.990 --> 31:41.686
- The environment here is good.
- Yes.

31:41.710 --> 31:42.966
There is another gate up front.

31:42.990 --> 31:45.006
It's a very long downhill
and extremely beautiful.

31:45.030 --> 31:46.931
- Let's take that way next time.
- Sure.

31:50.191 --> 31:52.310
Look, this is my studio.

31:52.310 --> 31:54.786
(Zhaozhaomumu Music Studio)

31:57.230 --> 31:59.567
Over here is our collection of work.

31:59.591 --> 32:01.451
(Works Display Panel)
Though not many...

32:06.151 --> 32:08.206
Our place, though not as large as yours,

32:08.230 --> 32:10.730
is still small and cozy enough.

32:11.470 --> 32:13.691
Gu Sheng, you're so loud.

32:13.790 --> 32:16.246
You woke me up
before I got enough sleep.

32:16.270 --> 32:17.891
My head is hurting.

32:24.351 --> 32:25.206
Should I talk?

32:25.230 --> 32:28.931
This sofa is so hard.
It gives me backaches.

32:29.710 --> 32:30.847
You can say whatever you want.

32:30.871 --> 32:32.470
But try not to sound like you...

32:32.470 --> 32:34.611
Specifically, don't sound
like Qiang Qingci.

32:47.391 --> 32:49.526
Why are you sleeping here?

32:49.550 --> 32:50.810
I forgot my keys.

32:52.270 --> 32:55.006
Then why didn't you turn on the AC?
In case catching a cold.

32:55.030 --> 32:56.810
Save energy. Who's he?

33:01.591 --> 33:06.050
He is my friend.

33:07.151 --> 33:08.411
A good friend.

33:10.911 --> 33:11.911
Hello.

33:14.151 --> 33:15.851
Have we met before?

33:18.111 --> 33:21.730
Probably not.

33:25.871 --> 33:29.010
Then why does your voice
sound so familiar?

33:31.750 --> 33:35.131
Familiar? It's just a common voice.

33:37.470 --> 33:38.970
I'll go brush my teeth now.

33:45.191 --> 33:47.526
It's fine. He's nice.

33:47.550 --> 33:48.230
Come over here. Sit.

33:48.230 --> 33:49.647
Stop chatting, Sheng.

33:49.671 --> 33:51.091
Clean up now.

33:51.191 --> 33:52.127
Wait a moment.

33:52.151 --> 33:54.010
It'll just take an hour.

34:00.231 --> 34:02.006
- Wait a moment.
- What?

34:02.030 --> 34:04.130
Isn't Qiang Qingci pursuing you?

34:04.351 --> 34:05.646
What's going on with you?

34:05.670 --> 34:08.970
You mustn't covet more
after obtaining something.

34:09.630 --> 34:10.606
It's not like that.

34:10.630 --> 34:11.927
What do you mean?

34:11.951 --> 34:13.767
Look at the way
you two are glancing at each other,

34:13.791 --> 34:15.771
so romantically ambiguous.

34:17.311 --> 34:20.486
Listen, my idol is a good person.

34:20.510 --> 34:22.446
I don't know
if he has any issues in terms of looks.

34:22.470 --> 34:24.486
But his character is impeccable.

34:24.510 --> 34:29.211
After all, he is Qiang Qingci,
the dream and ideal of many.

34:29.510 --> 34:30.771
I know.

34:30.871 --> 34:33.411
Even knowing that,
you still flirt with that guy?

34:38.070 --> 34:42.170
He's a senior at the school next door.

34:43.030 --> 34:46.291
The most dangerous word is "senior."

34:46.431 --> 34:48.046
You've never been a senior?

34:48.070 --> 34:50.411
I would never covet a junior sister.

34:50.791 --> 34:53.371
Fine. I won't talk with you.
I'll go clean up.

35:01.470 --> 35:02.727
I'll do it. I'll do it.

35:02.751 --> 35:05.211
What's the point of inviting you over
if you have to work?

35:05.510 --> 35:06.247
It's okay.

35:06.271 --> 35:08.490
I have nothing to do
when sitting here. Move around.

35:44.110 --> 35:46.490
(How is my idol any inferior to him?)

35:48.871 --> 35:50.050
You are here.

35:55.951 --> 35:57.731
Why did you all come?

35:57.831 --> 35:59.566
Off Key said he had no money for food.

35:59.590 --> 36:01.211
We came to deliver food.

36:04.751 --> 36:06.731
Who is this?

36:09.831 --> 36:12.411
Off Key, your friend?

36:14.751 --> 36:15.966
My friend.

36:15.990 --> 36:18.046
Yes. It is her friend.

36:18.070 --> 36:20.690
He's a senior
from her neighboring school.

36:23.070 --> 36:25.371
- Hello.
- Hello.

36:26.351 --> 36:28.727
How can we
ask a guest to clean up in our studio?

36:28.751 --> 36:30.166
Come on. Let's all help.

36:30.190 --> 36:31.771
It's fine. No worries.

36:31.871 --> 36:33.927
Sheng, go keep your friend company.

36:33.951 --> 36:35.211
- Don't bother.
- Go.

36:35.791 --> 36:38.530
No. Stay still, everybody.

36:38.711 --> 36:39.966
It's my turn today.

36:39.990 --> 36:41.847
It was supposed to be
my cleaning day anyway.

36:41.871 --> 36:43.327
Silly girl.

36:43.351 --> 36:44.966
You're the only one following the rules.

36:44.990 --> 36:47.247
Off Key even had me
clean for him last week.

36:47.271 --> 36:49.126
Can you finish what you're saying?

36:49.150 --> 36:51.247
Why don't you mention
I treated you to a meal?

36:51.271 --> 36:52.646
Fold it yourself.

36:52.670 --> 36:53.927
Or, how about this?

36:53.951 --> 36:55.927
I'll treat you to a meal.

36:55.951 --> 36:57.530
Don't bother.

36:57.831 --> 36:59.367
We could eat at your school's cafeteria.

36:59.391 --> 37:01.287
- We'll use your card.
- Sure.

37:01.311 --> 37:03.411
I've been wanting to try
the saute spicy chicken.

37:03.831 --> 37:06.006
It is usually sold out by noon.

37:06.030 --> 37:07.731
Sold out again?

37:09.030 --> 37:10.931
I'll make it.

37:13.030 --> 37:14.166
It's too much trouble.

37:14.190 --> 37:15.566
Let's just order takeout.

37:15.590 --> 37:17.771
Takeout won't taste
as good as what I make.

37:21.030 --> 37:22.006
Gu Sheng has had it.

37:22.030 --> 37:24.010
She knows. You can ask her.

37:27.630 --> 37:30.530
Tastes really good indeed.

37:30.831 --> 37:33.086
Off Key, go with him to buy groceries.

37:33.110 --> 37:34.570
We'll clean up.

37:37.510 --> 37:39.526
Let's go then, neighbor senior.

37:39.550 --> 37:41.050
I'll wait for you outside.

37:41.110 --> 37:42.130
Alright.

37:42.550 --> 37:43.446
I'm heading out.

37:43.470 --> 37:45.050
- Give me.
- Okay.

37:47.150 --> 37:48.570
Please be careful.

37:52.110 --> 37:53.327
Who's him? He's chasing you?

37:53.351 --> 37:54.231
Looks pretty good.

37:54.231 --> 37:54.911
Quite serious.

37:54.911 --> 37:56.446
He's diligent, not delicate.

37:56.470 --> 37:57.566
He can also cook.

37:57.590 --> 37:58.927
How do you feel about it?

37:58.951 --> 38:00.411
Want a relationship?

38:02.030 --> 38:03.650
What about Qiang Qingci?

38:08.911 --> 38:11.291
Dude, you seem to have ulterior motives.

38:13.190 --> 38:13.966
You see it through?

38:13.990 --> 38:15.126
Nonsense.

38:15.150 --> 38:16.327
I am a man too.

38:16.351 --> 38:18.891
I see through your little schemes.

38:19.590 --> 38:22.010
How long have you been chasing her?

38:23.351 --> 38:24.530
A long time.

38:24.831 --> 38:26.086
But it's useless.

38:26.110 --> 38:29.811
To tell you the truth,
there are many people chasing her.

38:30.431 --> 38:31.490
Really?

38:32.030 --> 38:33.231
I guess I need to try harder then.

38:33.231 --> 38:34.771
It may be futile.

38:34.990 --> 38:37.207
She has a suitor who is quite famous.

38:37.231 --> 38:39.086
He's a famous dubbing actor.

38:39.110 --> 38:40.731
He has millions of fans.

38:40.911 --> 38:42.727
He's always dropping hints on his Weibo.

38:42.751 --> 38:44.530
His pursuit is quite high-profile.

38:45.510 --> 38:47.811
What do you do? Do you have a job?

38:48.670 --> 38:49.811
I am a doctor.

38:50.351 --> 38:51.570
A doctor.

38:52.190 --> 38:54.166
Grandma, where are you going?

38:54.190 --> 38:56.126
I'm almost home around the corner.

38:56.150 --> 38:56.911
Let me help you.

38:56.911 --> 38:58.090
It's fine.

38:58.751 --> 39:00.650
Young man, you are kind.

39:00.951 --> 39:02.331
You're welcome, grandma.

39:03.791 --> 39:04.791
This is my home.

39:04.791 --> 39:05.767
This one, right?

39:05.791 --> 39:07.371
Yes. This one.

39:08.431 --> 39:11.807
(A doctor is a good job indeed.)

39:11.831 --> 39:13.871
(He looks good,
does housework and can cook.)

39:13.871 --> 39:14.590
Take care, grandma.

39:14.590 --> 39:16.767
(Even if I am
a diehard fan of Qiang Qingci, )

39:16.791 --> 39:18.966
(I am also a buddy of Sheng's.)

39:18.990 --> 39:20.470
- It's fine. There you up.
- Okay.

39:20.470 --> 39:23.367
(If I have to choose,
Sheng is more important.)

39:23.391 --> 39:24.431
- Bye, grandma.
- Thank you.

39:24.431 --> 39:26.851
- (Forget it. Let's see who she likes.)
- You're welcome.

39:39.630 --> 39:41.327
You came all the way to see me.

39:41.351 --> 39:43.126
You've been cleaning and cooking too.

39:43.150 --> 39:44.570
I'm quite embarrassed.

39:45.351 --> 39:48.006
Didn't I promise to make
saute spicy chicken for you at noon?

39:48.030 --> 39:49.446
Since everyone wants to eat it,

39:49.470 --> 39:50.731
isn't it just right?

39:51.190 --> 39:53.727
They have always been very good to me.

39:53.751 --> 39:55.727
We are a nobody club,

39:55.751 --> 39:57.731
but we get along well.

39:58.110 --> 39:59.211
I can tell.

39:59.871 --> 40:03.407
Actually, Off Key and Guai
don't earn much.

40:03.431 --> 40:04.887
Especially Off Key.

40:04.911 --> 40:08.126
He can't afford to rent a house.

40:08.150 --> 40:09.807
He lives in the company's dormitory.

40:09.831 --> 40:11.606
Occasionally, he would
come to live here.

40:11.630 --> 40:14.331
It's because
one of his roommates got married.

40:14.391 --> 40:15.367
Once his wife comes,

40:15.391 --> 40:18.570
he would willingly give up
space for their family gathering.

40:21.311 --> 40:24.367
We used to be a small club too.

40:24.391 --> 40:27.530
At first, everyone
pooled money to rent a house.

40:27.990 --> 40:30.407
Then, we got more and more dubbing work.

40:30.431 --> 40:31.851
So things improved.

40:32.231 --> 40:34.606
Later on, everyone started working.

40:34.630 --> 40:36.931
When we had salaries,
things got even better.

40:40.030 --> 40:40.670
May not be enough.

40:40.670 --> 40:41.851
Add a little more.

40:41.951 --> 40:43.911
I have hinted enough at you

40:43.911 --> 40:45.207
to learn cooking.

40:45.231 --> 40:47.086
We bought so many
kitchen utensils and seasonings.

40:47.110 --> 40:49.086
The first time cooking happens
when the guest comes over.

40:49.110 --> 40:50.367
Is that appropriate?

40:50.391 --> 40:51.570
Did you hear that?

40:51.990 --> 40:53.566
My cooking skills are not good.

40:53.590 --> 40:55.530
Even if I cook,
you don't like to eat it.

40:56.030 --> 40:57.811
I think he's not bad.

40:57.871 --> 40:59.010
I think so too.

40:59.911 --> 41:01.207
Yes.

41:01.231 --> 41:03.247
But I always feel something is off.

41:03.271 --> 41:05.407
The other day,
I saw my idol, Qiang Qingci,

41:05.431 --> 41:06.970
posted a new song on Weibo.

41:07.070 --> 41:10.570
- It's said they went to an exhibit.
- Really?

41:11.311 --> 41:12.086
But...

41:12.110 --> 41:15.807
Sheng and Qiang Qingci
haven't met many times.

41:15.831 --> 41:18.086
I don't think sparks flew between them.

41:18.110 --> 41:19.580
They must have made it clear.

41:21.150 --> 41:22.331
Makes sense.

41:22.590 --> 41:24.771
Sheng is not someone who will two-time.

41:25.311 --> 41:27.247
It must be because
they don't have chemistry.

41:27.271 --> 41:29.966
That's why we have the senior
who can cook saute spicy chicken.

41:29.990 --> 41:33.086
No. I just knew

41:33.110 --> 41:35.251
they had known each other for long.

41:37.951 --> 41:42.211
- Rice wine.
- Rice wine. Here you go.

41:45.791 --> 41:46.811
Smells great.

41:47.030 --> 41:48.331
So good.

41:49.271 --> 41:52.291
Learn from this skill.

41:54.951 --> 41:56.847
I'm a bit behind
in preparing the things below.

41:56.871 --> 41:57.927
Could you all help me?

41:57.951 --> 41:58.887
- I'm in.
- Okay.

41:58.911 --> 42:00.646
I always help my mom at home.

42:00.670 --> 42:01.486
I can do it, too.

42:01.510 --> 42:02.970
What dishes are there?

42:03.550 --> 42:05.046
There are cumin lamb

42:05.070 --> 42:06.006
and belt noodles.

42:06.030 --> 42:07.166
I've also prepared some kebobs.

42:07.190 --> 42:09.130
Once they're done, I will take them out.

42:09.431 --> 42:11.211
We haven't decided on the vegetables.

42:11.951 --> 42:13.931
How about spicy and sour cabbage?

42:13.990 --> 42:16.490
- Impressive.
- Here.

42:21.751 --> 42:25.050
The last main dish, the belt noodles.

42:25.431 --> 42:26.391
My favorite.

42:26.391 --> 42:26.911
While it's hot.

42:26.911 --> 42:27.431
I want it.

42:27.431 --> 42:29.451
- Eat up.
- Let me have a taste. I'm starving.

42:30.510 --> 42:32.891
How is it? Is it delicious?

42:33.911 --> 42:36.110
It is much better
than the ones made outside.

42:36.110 --> 42:37.086
Really?

42:37.110 --> 42:39.247
- If it's good, eat more.
- Right.

42:39.271 --> 42:40.811
Try this quickly. Try this.

42:40.871 --> 42:44.050
- Delicious.
- The chicken isn't dry at all.

42:45.911 --> 42:48.711
Why don't you come over
every week, senior next door?

42:48.711 --> 42:50.207
I'll do the grocery shopping.

42:50.231 --> 42:52.887
Senior, I will cover
all of Sheng's duty days.

42:52.911 --> 42:56.247
As long as you come once a week.

42:56.271 --> 42:57.287
I'd like to.

42:57.311 --> 42:58.526
But I don't usually have time.

42:58.550 --> 42:59.931
It's rare for today.

43:00.871 --> 43:02.970
- Sheng.
- Sheng.

43:06.751 --> 43:08.767
He did not lie to you.

43:08.791 --> 43:10.530
He is really busy.

43:10.711 --> 43:12.566
Then I have to eat a few more bites.

43:12.590 --> 43:14.727
Otherwise, I don't know
when I will eat next.

43:14.751 --> 43:16.291
Next time, hmm.

43:16.431 --> 43:17.690
Let me think about it.

43:18.590 --> 43:20.847
What about two weeks later?

43:20.871 --> 43:22.086
- Really?
- Really?

43:22.110 --> 43:23.606
If I don't have to work overtime.

43:23.630 --> 43:24.486
Deal.

43:24.510 --> 43:25.610
I'll wait for you.

43:28.150 --> 43:29.251
Have a taste.

43:59.102 --> 44:02.855
♪ Where should I start
about millions of dawns and dusks ♪

44:02.855 --> 44:04.035
♪ Depict a stroke ♪

44:04.035 --> 44:05.063
♪ Of rain before the mountain ♪

44:05.063 --> 44:07.462
♪ Stars beyond the sky ♪

44:07.486 --> 44:11.591
♪ Bit by bit, it outlines
yesterday and today ♪

44:11.591 --> 44:14.151
♪ And you with
picturesque eyebrows and eyes ♪

44:14.151 --> 44:16.635
♪ Jointly create the mood ♪

44:17.694 --> 44:21.415
♪ The rain and fog
over the mountains are intriguing ♪

44:21.415 --> 44:22.823
♪ It seems I can't get enough of seeing ♪

44:22.823 --> 44:25.912
♪ The once inexhaustible journey ♪

44:25.912 --> 44:26.951
♪ On this journey ♪

44:26.951 --> 44:28.647
♪ The stars accompany me
along thousands of miles ♪

44:28.647 --> 44:30.822
♪ I walk down with you ♪

44:30.822 --> 44:35.483
♪ Spending dawns and dusks together
for a hundred years ♪

44:35.550 --> 44:37.447
♪ Just like ♪

44:37.447 --> 44:38.377
♪ When the clouds are low ♪

44:38.377 --> 44:40.002
♪ It rains ♪

44:40.002 --> 44:44.466
♪ I was moved when you sing softly ♪

44:44.466 --> 44:48.199
♪ Since then, I hear stars every night ♪

44:48.199 --> 44:49.287
♪ And rains at midnight ♪

44:49.287 --> 44:53.760
♪ I could hear you among millions of voices ♪

44:53.760 --> 44:56.235
♪ All other voices fade away ♪

44:56.235 --> 44:58.641
♪ I hear your monologue ♪

44:58.641 --> 45:03.001
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

45:03.001 --> 45:05.447
♪ Like understanding
the implied meaning of a picture ♪

45:05.447 --> 45:08.079
♪ Understanding the emotion in your eyes ♪

45:08.079 --> 45:12.103
♪ Feels new even after several times ♪

45:12.103 --> 45:14.759
♪ Among the millions of people ♪

45:14.759 --> 45:17.357
♪ I hear your voice ♪

45:17.357 --> 45:21.250
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

45:21.250 --> 45:23.942
♪ A sky full of stars
all over the mountains and fields ♪

45:23.942 --> 45:26.535
♪ You are my whole world ♪

45:26.535 --> 45:33.435
♪ Slowly spending
dawns and dusks with you ♪
